Name: global

Synonyms: global, globally, global variable, global property,
global properties

Type: glossary

Description:
Pertaining to the whole application environment, rather than a single
<handler> or <object(glossary)>.

A global <variable|variable's> value is available to any <handler>; a
global <property> affects the overall environment, not just one
<object(glossary)>. 

References: property (glossary), handler (glossary), variable (glossary),
object (glossary)

Tags: properties

